Package: proxysnps
Title: Get proxy SNPs for a SNP in the 1000 Genomes Project
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Kamil", "Slowikowski", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
    "kslowikowski@fas.harvard.edu") )
Description: This package implements functions to query remote VCF files. You
    can use it to find proxy SNPs in linkage disequilibrium with SNPs of
    interest or to calculate allele frequencies in different populations.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/slowkow/proxysnps
BugReports: https://github.com/slowkow/proxysnps/issues
Imports:
    RCurl
